{"word":"G1303 - διατίθεμαι - diatíthemai - dee-at-ith'-em-ahee - Appoint","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διατίθεμαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">diatíthemai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dee-at-ith'-em-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Appoint</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஏற்படுத்து, சாசனத்தை எழுது"},{"paragraph":"to place separately, dispose, arrange, appoint, to arrange, dispose of, one's own affairs, to make a covenant, enter into covenant, with one"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Middle voice from <a href=\"#/G1223 - διά - diá - dee-ah'/1223\">G1223</a> and <a href=\"#/G5087 - τίθημι - títhēmi - tith'-ay-mee/5087\">G5087</a>; to <i>put apart</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>dispose</i> (by assignment, compact or bequest): - appoint, make, testator.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1242/1242\">G1242</a>, <a href=\"#/G1303/1303\">G1303</a>"}]}